g|Shana Fring]]\n|[[Aeri\u00e9l Miranda]]\n| \"Out of the Frying Pan, Into the Inferno\"\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || {{CGuest|Guest}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[#Eddie Lamb|Eddie Lamb]]\n| [[Reggie Austin (actor)|Reggie Austin]]\n| \"Will The Circle Be Broken?\"\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}} || {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CGuest|Guest}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[#Arthur Hackett|Arthur Hackett]]\n| John O'Brien\n| \"Kingdom of the Blind\"\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}} || {{CGuest|Guest}} || {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || {{CGuest|Guest}} || {{CNone}} || {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[#Gabriel Holbrook|Gabriel Holbrook]]\n|[[Sean Faris]]\n| \"'A' is for A-l-i-v-e\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[#Linda Tanner|Linda Tanner]]\n|[[Roma Maffia]]\n| \"Face Time\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}} || colspan=\"3\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[#Carla Grunwald|Carla Grunwald]]\n|[[Meg Foster]]\n| \"Under the Gun\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}} || {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || {{CGuest|Guest}} || {{CNone}} || {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[#Travis Hobbs|Travis Hobbs]]\n|[[Luke Kleintank]]\n| \"Bring Down the Hoe\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}} || {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || {{CGuest|Guest}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |[[#Jake|Jake]]\n|[[Ryan Guzman]]\n| \"Turn of the Shoe\"\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}} || {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || colspan=\"3\" {{CNone}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[#Kenneth DiLaurentis|Kenneth DiLaurentis]]\n| Jim Abele\n| \"Crazy\" \n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}} || {{CGuest|Guest}} || {{CNone}} || colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}} || {{CNone}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[#Andrew Campbell|Andrew Campbell]]\n| [[Brandon Jones (actor)|Brandon Jones]]\n| \"Mona-Mania\" \n| colspan=\"2\" {{CNone}} || colspan=\"2\